_sText:
Description: de_black_ops was designed at its base to be a rush or die map.
The map itself is large designed for 15-64 players. frame rates are high in all areas of the map.
Keep moving and learn the map there are alot of options on where to go and how to get there.
The map is a dark spooky abandoned military base. night vision works great and there are pleanty 
of areas where flash bangs and smoke gernades work perfectly.
